$$
K_{C C P}=\sum_{i}m a x\{E B R M_{\mathrm{i}}-I M_{\mathrm{i}}-D F_{\mathrm{i}};\mathbf{0}\}\cdot R W\cdot c a p t i a l r a t i o
$$
where:
EBRMi
$\mathbf{\Sigma}=\mathbf{\Sigma}$ exposure value before risk mitigation that is equal to the exposure value of the CCP to clearing member i arising from all the contracts and transactions with that clearing member, calculated without taking into account the collateral posted by that clearing member;
IMi $\mathbf{\Sigma}=\mathbf{\Sigma}$ the initial margin posted to the CCP by clearing member i;
DFi $\mathbf{\Sigma}=\mathbf{\Sigma}$ the pre-funded contribution of clearing member i;
